<br>
1)<br>
Ancient: Gift of Aegolism CLE 60<br>
-Group: Increase Hitpoints: 1300 <br>
-Group: Increase Armor Class: 69<br>
<br>
2)<br>
Marzin's Mark CLE 60<br>
-Group: Increase Total Hit Points by 700<br>
<br>
3)<br>
Visions of Granduer ENC 60<br>
-Target: Increase Attack Speed (58%) <br>
-Target: Increase Agility (40) <br>
-Target: Increase Dexterity (25) <br>
-Target: Increase ATK (15)<br>
<br>
4)<br>
Ancient: Feral Avatar SHM 60<br>
-Target: Increase Strength (120) <br>
-Target: Increase Dexterity (120) <br>
-Target: Increase ATK (120) <br>
-Target: Increase Agility (120)<br>
<br>
5)<br>
Khura's Focusing SHM 60<br>
-Group: Increase Hitpoints (430)<br>
-Group: Increase Dexterity (60)<br>
-Group: Increase Strength (67)<br>
<br>
6)<br>
Talisman of the Brute SHM 57<br>
-Group: Increase Stamina (50)<br>
<br>
7)<br>
Talisman of Kragg SHM 55<br>
-Target: Increase Hitpoints (380)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
Regrowth of Dah Khura SHM 60<br>
-Group: Increase Health Regeneration (15)<br>
<br>
9)<br>
Ancient: Legacy of Blades DRU 60<br>
-Group: Damage Shield (36)<br>
<br>
10)<br>
Brell's Mountainous Barrier PAL 60<br>
-Target: Increase Hitpoints (225)<br>
<br>
11)<br>
Call of the Predator RNG 60<br>
-Group: Increase ATK (40)<br>
<br>
12)<br>
Call of Earth RNG 50<br>
-Target: Damage Shield (4) <br>
-Target: Increase AC (26)<br>
<br>
13)<br>
Force of Nature RNG 49<br>
-Target: Regenerate (5hp per tick) <br>
-Target: Damage Shield (3) <br>
-Target: Increase ATK (15)<br>
<br>
14)<br>
Warsong of the Vah Shir BRD 60<br>
Increase Haste by 25% (Above Cap)<br>
<br>
15)<br>
Chorus of Replenishment BRD 58<br>
-Area Effect: Increase Health Regeneration (12 per tick) <br>
-Area Effect: Increase Mana Regeneration (13 per tick) <br>
-Area Effect: Increase Stamina Regeneration (12 per tick) <br>
<br>
Using that lineup, one would gain:<br>
<br>
HP: 3035<br>
AC: 95<br>
ATK: 175<br>
STR: 187<br>
STA: 50<br>
AGI: 160<br>
DEX: 205<br>
<br>
HP Regen: 27<br>
Mana Regen: 13<br>
Haste %: 58 +25% above cap<br>
Dmg Sheild: 40<br>
Stam Regen: 12<br>
<br>
Which is coo because then ya only need 68str, 205sta, 95agi, and 50dex to get to 255 in all stats LOL<br>
<br>
Also, 7, 11, 12, and 13 probably have better options.<br>
(like shammy potions, item effects, etc.<br>
